@host = http://localhost:5106

### Start load test (default 1000 msg/s)
POST {{host}}/load-test/start

### Start load test with custom rate
POST {{host}}/load-test/start?rate=5000

### Stop load test
POST {{host}}/load-test/stop

### Get current metrics (publish rate, errors, backpressure)
GET {{host}}/metrics

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
